title: Pig Lead Receipts for St. Louis, MO-IL
notes:
Data For 1865 Were Computed By Adding River And Railroad Receipts. Data For 1880, 1903, And 1924 Were Furnished Directly To NBER From The Merchants Exchange. Source: Merchants Exchange Of St. Louis (Formerly Union Merchants Exchange), Annual Statements Of The Trade And Commerce Of St. Louis.

This NBER data series m01139 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 1 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter01.html.
